SEARCH, INSTALL & UNINSTALL SOFTWARE
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EwezNTJ-Lj0
apt-cache search snake - search snake software to find the exact name of the package or use the manual
					   - manual - folder/computer/usr/share/applications (all installed software)
					   - search on the software name, copy and paste in the desktop
sudo apt-get install snake4 - install software snake4(package name)
sudo apt-get remove snake4

